			$ sum *.msi
			55600  2397 JSummer-0.0.6.0-java.msi
			10915  6651 JSummer-0.0.6.0-native.msi
			$ cksum *.msi
			938227130 2454016 JSummer-0.0.6.0-java.msi
			991995451 6810624 JSummer-0.0.6.0-native.msi
			cksum: CRC checksum and byte counts
			sum: checksum and block counts:
					BSD sum algorithm, use 1K blocks
					System V sum algorithm, use 512 bytes blocks
		
